{"tid":557147,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"紅十字會：車禍取用血包不算多　惟庫存低仍籲捐血","createTime":"2018-02-11T05:30:02.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-11T08:33:38.000Z","uid":5195,"like":0,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"817158b2c18e1774475fa2b6e62165e16a1b73de","tid":557147,"uid":5195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-11T05:30:02.000Z","msg":"大埔公路昨（10日）發生巴士翻側奪命車禍，釀成19死逾60傷慘劇。紅十字會輸血服務中心行政及醫務總監李卓廣表示，車禍後有醫院向中心索取幾十包血液，因有數名傷者出現嚴重骨折及內出血等需要輸血。<br />\n<br />\n對於有網傳車禍急需血液急救，發出「緊急呼籲」消息，李卓廣則指，是熱心市民自發行為，但血庫存量向來不高，呼籲適宜捐血的市民，可趁假日天氣好，到血站捐血。<br />\n<br />\n李卓廣表示，昨日車禍後，中心向收症多的醫院供應數十包血，數量未算太大，會繼續密切留意醫院情況。他續指，血庫存量向來不高，尤其對A型及O型血液需求大，呼籲適宜捐血的市民，趁假日到血站捐血救人，各中心亦會延長服務時間。而香港紅十字會網站及Facebook專頁，暫未就車禍發出緊急呼籲捐血消息。"},{"pid":"a3447eb8cf18d707c4510cebc1d220ce73421bb2","tid":557147,"uid":35815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-11T05:31:18.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"e1b9295f0142f254eaad1fffadd6637f67660c64","tid":557147,"uid":72457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-11T05:32:34.000Z","msg":"出血個D都死哂<br />\n又叫人捐血救大陸人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8270ad40b4943ef064a259f4d423aa5edea09b22","tid":557147,"uid":8048,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-11T05:33:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6f503f77b99b10738ca9db6b55edbf2d03160e98","tid":557147,"uid":105059,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-11T08:33:38.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=WLIrfbaxq30&amp;feature=youtu.be&amp;t=249\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DWLIrfbaxq30%26feature%3Dyoutu.be%26t%3D249&d=nDiTdU8cgH%2FcSBu6VtOslf6YfqAiA4jm3R2Vm1010vU%3D&h=23327803\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=WLIrfbaxq30&amp;feature=youtu.be&amp;t=249</a>"}]}